# Email Configuration
# Currently using Ethereal Email (testing service) - emails are NOT sent to real addresses
# Preview URLs are logged to the server console
# 
# To send real emails, configure the following SMTP settings:
# SMTP_HOST=smtp.gmail.com (or smtp.office365.com for Outlook, smtp.sendgrid.net for SendGrid)
# SMTP_PORT=587
# SMTP_SECURE=false (true for port 465)
# SMTP_USER=your-email@gmail.com
# SMTP_PASS=your-app-password (use App Password for Gmail, not regular password)
#
# Example for Gmail:
# SMTP_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
# SMTP_PORT=587
# SMTP_SECURE=false
# SMTP_USER=yourname@gmail.com
# SMTP_PASS=your-16-char-app-password
#
# Example for SendGrid:
# SMTP_HOST=smtp.sendgrid.net
# SMTP_PORT=587
# SMTP_SECURE=false
# SMTP_USER=apikey
# SMTP_PASS=your-sendgrid-api-key